abstract: Texas health department cuts off $600,000 in federal funding to Houston affiliate of Planned Parenthood for nearly three-decade-old HIV prevention program.
lead_paragraph: The state health department is cutting off federal funding to a Houston affiliate of Planned Parenthood for a nearly three-decade-old H.I.V. prevention program.

headline.main: Texas: Funding Cut to Planned Parenthood
